OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPope Francis Urbi et Orbi  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faddress: World ignoring    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhuge tragedies             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pope Francis has warned that the world 
OL,6, is becoming so desensitised to crises  
OL,7, and suffering that they are now        
OL,8, happening while hardly being noticed.  
OL,10,FIn his annual Christmas Day message,   
OL,11,Fthe pontiff pointed to ongoing turmoil 
OL,12,Fin Syria, Yemen and Iraq, as well as in
OL,13,Fareas of Africa, Europe and Asia.      
OL,15,FHe also said the effects of the        
OL,16,Fpandemic threatened efforts to resolve 
OL,17,Fconflicts on an international level.   
OL,19,FHe spoke outdoors again this year after
OL,20,Fmaking his speech indoors last year.   
